Bayes' Theorem of Probability With Tree Diagrams & Venn Diagrams 
- https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OByl4RJxnKA 

P(A/B) = P(B/A) P(A) / P(B) = P(A and B) / P(B)
P(B/A) = P(A/B) P(B) / P(A) = P(B and A) / P(A) 

